erromagnetic state emerges in Pb$_2$CoOsO$_6$, distinct from the one under\nambient pressure, thus showing a discontinuity in $dT_N/dP$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2020 16:57:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
