ontrast nor the shift of the\nhot spot on isobars, and propose solutions to to recover the true hot-spot\nshift and day/night contrast.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2020 10:30:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-18"}
