ck hole binaries. We point out that a clear signature for massive\nP-stars would be the detection of wobble frequencies in the gravitational wave\nstrain amplitude in the post-merger phase of two coalescing massive compact\nobjects with unequal masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2020 14:27:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2020 10:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-10"}
